title: HangARoo v1.1 + Cheats [Sbyky]
description:
Hangaroo is a fun reinterpretation of the classic hangman game! Guess each letter in the phrase to form a full word! Be careful though, for every letter you get wrong, the poor kangaroo will be one step closer to his demise! So be careful, and use all your wits to succeed in this clever puzzle game!

Instructions: Use mouse or keyboard.

Note: I've always wanted to make an organised solution list of all the phrases in this addictive game, today i was successful so i decided to share, i hope you like it.
